Well if you want your message edited i'll explain it! 

We using '$editIn' Yeah Simple!

Q: How to use it?
A: Easy It Is $editIn[times;New Message]

Examples:

$editIn[2s;Hello]
It means your message will edited after 2seconds!
S= Seconds, H= Hours, D= Day.

Before Without Using Embed, Now I'll Show How To Using With Embed!

$editEmbedIn[time;title;message;footer;color]

Q: Is it same like $editIn?
A: Yeah is it
